{"tid":356912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★被上司責駡 80後跳樓亡！","createTime":"2017-08-12T12:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T08:42:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7a757c8636b54e323e314e0974fabae23654053","tid":356912,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:58:59.000Z","msg":"葵涌男子跳樓亡。早上9時半，葵喜街1至11號達利國際中心3樓平台傳出惡臭味，姓郭(59歲)男保安員接報查看，揭發一名姓馬(29歲)男子伏在平台，立即報警求助，救護員接報趕至，檢驗後證實他已身亡。警方經初步調查，得悉他近日因工作壓力問題而不開心，在現場未有檢獲遺書，相信他自天台躍下，事件無可疑，案件列作有人從高處墮下。據悉，馬因被上司責駡而鬱鬱不歡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170812/bkn-20170812101510958-0812_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170812%2Fbkn-20170812101510958-0812_00822_001.html&d=98m4kCksxFEIJSHFkFyK%2BviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7155e677\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170812/bkn-20170812101510958-0812_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"14cbd024f684addc6dac05bc8d56d9fc74b7a83b","tid":356912,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"返工 不了"},{"pid":"4f6d6f9bb5aae91e18f77c24c8f4428bfe6ca2bf","tid":356912,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cbf94dada6b8ba5c44e748b907c1a4a3f4c7ac2","tid":356912,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"廢，日日比人屌都冇事"},{"pid":"fb637f2111596858caea0a025aa735c71e54b570","tid":356912,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:28:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廢，日日比人屌都冇事</blockquote>唔係人人做得慣奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f458ecb33bd3a25fbbf6f2717e1595d83389581f","tid":356912,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廢，日日比人屌都冇事</blockquote>唔係人人做得慣奴隸<img src=\"/assets/